{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the freight trains, which are quite long, they were empty because they were going to-- to pick up the ammunition and all-- all the things that they need on the-- the front.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The front was quite far away from that place in Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we-- we just listened for the-- for the sounds of the train, and definitely the train came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because of the hill, the train had to slow down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the train slowed down, so we jumped on-- on one of the train carriages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, there were the freight train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were-- he, this guy and me, on separate trains or separate carriages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this way, we came to-- to Lwow, to Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and there, we-- we went out, outside, and where the civilians were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I-- we were going just straight to the-- we-- we-- we thought that there will be a train to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we thought that my-- my Lilian already is in Warsaw because they departed the day before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we're going on-- on the platform just openly like that, suddenly I noticed there was a-- a train standing there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly, I notice that somebody is waving from a-- from a window of the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- coming closer, I notice that was my Lilian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So apparently, there was something on-- on the tracks of the-- of-- of-- for that train, that the train didn't depart yesterday while-- how it should, but is departing the next-- after.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next day after.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she gave me-- of course, she was not-- not alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in company with those people from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she-- I understood right away that I should not come and see her.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
